Package: jaspBlinding
Type: Package
Title: Analysis Blinding for JASP
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-07-13
Author: JASP Team
Website: jasp-stats.org
Maintainer: JASP Team <info@jasp-stats.org>
Description: A JASP module providing analysis blinding (masking and scrambling) via the R package vazul, to reduce confirmation bias during confirmatory data analysis.
